AT THE REQUEST OF:
Montelena Master Community Association
4645 E Cotton Gin Loop
Phoenix, AZ 85040
(602) 437-4777
NOTICE AND CLAIM OF LIEN
Jodi Phelps, being first and duly sworn, deposes and says as follows:
Unofficial
2ºDocument
50
es
1. That she/he is an authorized agent of Montelena Master Community Association, an Arizona Corporation, being a Homeowner's Association
organized to own, operate and manage the commonly held facilities of Montelena Master Community Association.
2. That the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions are a covenant running with and binding the land in said subdivision; that the
Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions impose annual assessment on individual parcels of property within said subdivision and create a lien of
assessment in order to collect delinquent assessments; the assessment is both a lien against the real property and the personal obligation of the
record owner or purchaser of said real property.
3. Upon information and belief, the record owner or purchaser of Account #142 is Lewis Blankenship, the following real property situated in the
county of Maricopa, State of Arizona:
Lot 142, MONTELENA, according to the plat of record in the office of the County Recorder of Maricopa County, Arizona, in
Book 671 of Maps, Page 44, Dedication Recorded as 2004-1179426 of Official Records, and Affidavits of Correction Recorded
as 2005-1223262 of Official Records and as 2005-1512000 of Official Records and Re-Recorded as 2005-1740909 of Official
Records.
4. That the assessments on said real property are delinquent in the amount of $991.51. being due and presently unpaid.
5. The lien claimed against Lot # 142 is of a continuing nature and the amount stated as due and owing in Paragraph 4 will increase, and
continue to increase, if Owner(s) continues nonpayment of assessments in the future. The increases will be comprised of future unpaid
assessments, late fees, interest, costs of collection, other amounts as authorized under the Declaration and, if applicable, attomeys' fees.
6. This claim of lien is being made pursuant to the Declaration and is being recorded to inform the public of the current amount of said lien, and
is not a waiver of any prior lien on Lot # 142, which pursuant to the Declaration existed before the recording of this notice. A copy of this lien is
being sent to the Owners at their last known mailing address(cs).
7. This is an attempt to collect a debt and any information obtained can be used for that purpose.
IN WITNESS HEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand this 4th day of April.20227
STATE OF ARIZONA )
) ss.
COUNTY OF MARICOPA )
Authorized Agent
AZCLOP-80164
SUBSCRIBED AND SWORN to before me on this 4th day of April 2022, by Jodi Phelps.
My commission expires:
fillling Roger 2
Notary Phblic
LIBBY ROGERS
Notary Public - State of Artzona
MARICOPA COUNTY
Commission # 604549
Expires March 23, 2025
